---
config:
  layout: elk
---
flowchart LR
    FleetCustomer["👤 Fleet Customer<br><small>B2B Company User (SSO)</small>"] -- Login, select vehicle,<br>browse & buy services --> Spryker["🛒 Scania Service Shop<br>(Spryker B2B Marketplace)<br><small>POC — Scania sole merchant</small>"]
    BackOfficeUser["👤 Back Office User<br><small>Scania internal</small>"] -- Manage orders,<br>catalog, config --> Spryker
    Merchant["👤 Merchant<br><small>Scania-licensed provider</small>"] -. Future: fulfil services .-> Spryker

    Spryker -- Authenticate (SSO),<br>fetch customer/roles/products --> CIAM["🔐 CIAM (My Scania)<br><small>External — SSO / IdP</small>"]
    CIAM -- Tokens, name, email,<br>company, country, roles --> Spryker
    Spryker -- Fetch vehicles/assets<br>(live, paginated) --> FMAT["🚚 FMAT<br><small>External — Fleet Asset Mgmt</small>"]
    Spryker -- Post-order notify:<br>order created (async);<br>payment+activation (async, future) --> FMAT
    Spryker -- Fetch compatible services<br>+ prices per vehicle --> SECM["🧰 SECM<br><small>External — Service Catalog & Pricing</small>"]
    Spryker -- Fetch service details:<br>description, images<br>(external configurator, future) --> PIMSPISA["📦 PIM-SPISA<br><small>External — Service Details/Config</small>"]
    Spryker -- Order confirmation --> SMTP["✉️ SMTP<br><small>External — Email delivery</small>"]
    SMTP -- Confirmation email --> FleetCustomer

    FleetCustomer:::userStyle
    BackOfficeUser:::userStyle
    Merchant:::futureStyle
    Spryker:::systemStyle
    CIAM:::externalStyle
    FMAT:::externalStyle
    SECM:::externalStyle
    PIMSPISA:::externalStyle
    SMTP:::externalStyle
    classDef userStyle fill:#e1f5ff,stroke:#0366d6,stroke-width:2px
    classDef systemStyle fill:#E67E22,stroke:#c0392b,stroke-width:3px,color:#fff
    classDef externalStyle fill:#95A5A6,stroke:#7f8c8d,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    classDef futureStyle fill:#d5d8dc,stroke:#7f8c8d,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray:5 5,color:#555
